nexpected icing on the cake.  Thank you!  And as for the beet-feta tart, would you believe that I&#8217;d almost forgotten about it?  I&#8217;m long overdue for one&#8230;  </></>And Rob, you&#8217;re killing me!  The < HREF="http://www.vegatransports.com.au/AustralianStarwars/TRaider.jpg" REL="nofollow">sand people<> from <>Star Wars<>?  You nailed it.</p>
